===Alternative spellings===
Over 60 different spellings of the name have been recorded, including the following. (Reference: ''Macquarie Aboriginal Words'', [[w:Macquarie University|Macquarie University]], 1994, paperback ISBN 0-949757-79-9, chapter 5.)

* [[Wiradhuri]]
* [[Waradgeri]]
* [[Wooragurie]]
* [[Wirrathuri]]
* [[Wiraiari]]

===Proper noun===
'''Wiradjuri'''

# An [[indigenous]] people of [[Australia]] who live in a large area of [[New South Wales]] west of the [[w:Blue Mountains|Blue Mountains]].
# The [[language]] of these people.

